    <IsekaiLeveling.SkillTree.PassiveTreeDef>
        <defName>PassiveTree_Crafter</defName>
        <label>Crafter</label>
        <treeClass>Crafter</treeClass>
        <treeDescription>Masters of creation who bend raw materials to their will. Five constellations radiate from the crafter's core — each honing a different facet of their boundless ingenuity. The higher your natural Crafting skill, the more Masterwork Insight amplifies your work speed.</treeDescription>
        <classGimmick>MasterworkInsight</classGimmick>
        <classGimmickName>Masterwork Insight</classGimmickName>
        <classGimmickDescription>The Crafter's deep understanding of materials compounds with natural skill. Work speed scales with Crafting skill level — the higher their innate talent, the more the passive tree amplifies output. Masterwork Insight scales along the Mastercraft Path. Tier 1 (Apprentice's Eye): up to +15% at Crafting 20. Tier 2 (Journeyman's Hand): up to +30%. Tier 3 (Master's Touch): up to +50%. Tier 4 (Grand Master): up to +75%. Skill is the foundation — mastery is the reward.</classGimmickDescription>

